          "date": "2020-10-14 08:31:05.000000000",
          "tz": 480
        },
        "subject": "LU-14032 osd: create agent inode with proper GID",
        "message": "LU-14032 osd: create agent inode with proper GID\n\nIf some parent directory is set as S_ISGID, the agent inode for\nthe remote stripe directory in it will be created with its GID as\nits parent GID during creation, but it is restore as current_fsgid\nafter the creation, which cause the group quota discrepancy.\n\nChange-Id: I4398af06110d48be738888e20cac4d1c2f0b28fc\nSigned-off-by: Hongchao Zhang <hongchao@whamcloud.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
